reviews.text: This is a small Thai restaurant in Luen Wo Hui, Fanling, New Territories. It has street views outside. The Thai food here is nice and spicy and you can ask them to adjust the spiciness of the dishes. The food comes piping hot. The pineapple fried rice and spicy mussels are particularly good. Service is friendly and swift and the pricing is fair and reasonable. A good restaurant  to visit if you like spicy Thai food. Decor is ordinary.
